text: Shahenaz Jebreen (born 28 July 1992) is a Jordanian women's international footballer who plays as a midfielder. She is a member of the Jordan women's national football team. She was part of the team that competed at the 2010 Asian Games where she made an assist to Jordan's first goal in the tournament which was scored by teammate Maysa Jbarah and the 2014 AFC Women's Asian Cup.AFC Women's Asian Cup 2014 Final Competition Regulations On club level she played for Amman SC in Jordan. ==References== == External links == * Category:1992 births Category:Asian Games competitors for Jordan Category:FIFA Century Club Category:Footballers at the 2006 Asian Games Category:Footballers at the 2010 Asian Games Category:Footballers at the 2014 Asian Games Category:Jordan women's international footballers Category:Jordanian Muslims Category:Jordanian women's footballers Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Amman Category:Women's association football midfielders
